** rutherfod alpha particle scattering experiment: 1909
alpha particle: a double charged helium ion:
mass = 4u fast moving:

here inside experiments he take one very high beam alpha particle rays and beam it on GOLD FOIL  so few observation he got:
1) 90 percent of alpha particle passed throug the gold foil straight:
2)some of the alpha partcle deflected by small angle:
3)very few out of 1 in 12000 deflected by 180 degree

so hew reached conclusion and he suggested the four observatin:
1) here 99 perecnt light passes means the most of space is emty in atom:
2) here few alpha light diflected means there proton but its in very center and accmulated in nuvleus:
3)the size of nucleus is 10^5 small than atom:
4)mass concentrated in nucleus since the few light deficled with 180 degree means there is something very hard than alpha particle light that is all:

